   <concept id="FAR_22_1408" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">22.1408</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1452e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1474e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> Insert the clause at <xref href="52.222-36.dita#FAR_52_222_36"
                        base="i1056250"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-36</xref>, Equal Opportunity for Workers with Disabilities, in solicitations and contracts that exceed or are expected to exceed <ph rev="FAC 2025-06 October 1, 2025" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2024-001?>$20,000<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 22.1408 in paragraph (a) introductory text by removing “$15,000” and adding “$20,000” in its place.?></ph>, except when-</p>
               <ol id="d1452e26" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1474e19">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Both the performance of the work and the recruitment of workers will occur outside the United States, Puerto Rico, the Northern Mariana Islands, American Samoa, Guam, the U.S. Virgin Islands, and Wake Island; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1474e24">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                The Director of OFCCP or agency head has waived, in accordance with <xref href="22.1403.dita#FAR_22_1403"
                              base="i1095943"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">22.1403</xref>(a) or <xref href="22.1403.dita#FAR_22_1403"
                              base="i1095943"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">22.1403</xref>(b) all the terms of the clause.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1474e35">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            If the Director of OFCCP or agency head waives one or more (but not all) of the terms of the clause in accordance with <xref href="22.1403.dita#FAR_22_1403"
                        base="i1095943"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">22.1403</xref>(a) or <xref href="22.1403.dita#FAR_22_1403"
                        base="i1095943"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">22.1403</xref>(b), use the basic clause with its Alternate I.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
